==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exalted
<hw>Ex*alt"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Raised to lofty
height; elevated; extolled; refined; dignified; sublime.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Wiser far than Solomon,⟦br⟧
Of more <qex>exalted</qex> mind.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Time never fails to bring every <qex>exalted</qex> reputation to a
strict scrutiny.</q> <rj><qau>Ames.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Ex*alt"ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Ex*alt"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>exaltedness</xex> of some minds.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>T.
Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exalter</ent>⟦br⟧
